    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎来到 SIDE EYE HIGH ：点击式恐怖故事</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时间是1997年，地点在一个名叫瑞文维尔高地（Ravenvale Heights）的可疑小镇。接连不断的学生神秘死亡事件让整个社区陷入恐慌……而你，这位疲惫而愤世的前侦探，被派去伪装成一名“安全审查员”，调查真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>SideEye High</i> 是一款带有黑色幽默与成人主题的点击式冒险游戏，将90年代经典风格与现代调查机制相结合。检查每一条走廊、每一个储物柜、每一块沾满口香糖的地砖——因为在这所学校里，<i>一切</i> 都是证据。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一个主线谜团，数十条支线歧途</strong> – 解决主要案件，或陷入超过50个虚假的结局中，每个都有自己扭曲的小故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>没有失败状态</strong> – 无论如何，这场为期一周的调查都会结束，但你的选择——以及错过的线索——将决定最终的结果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>放大表面之下</strong> – 放大查看笔记、细小的线索，甚至窥视<i>物体背后</i>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每个物品都很重要</strong> – 几乎所有东西都可以检查和互动，从墙上的螺丝到地板上的划痕。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>时间是你的敌人</strong> – 每个动作都会消耗时间。决定哪些值得调查，哪些可以放弃。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成人黑色幽默</strong> – 带有90年代风格的讽刺，犀利、荒诞且令人不安地真实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>部分角色介绍：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103560/extras/a2c19bda2d10f163b7dd75d9e82fcb39.avif?t=1770272806\" width=616 height=308 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103560/extras/f099725af70cc3752a965bc47abe781a.avif?t=1770272806\" width=616 height=308 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103560/extras/e7bb1102913a2562f17f4987f46cf112.avif?t=1770272806\" width=616 height=308 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103560/extras/440be4481ea04637b0f91bfaeaf6ec8d.avif?t=1770272806\" width=616 height=308 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103560/extras/919446aa727d7783323abd4430c90193.avif?t=1770272806\" width=616 height=308 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103560/extras/65a72f8ae16946040356b42c43a9d83f.avif?t=1770272806\" width=616 height=308 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103560/extras/5891e610212941a59e1932e859cb0eed.avif?t=1770272806\" width=616 height=308 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103560/extras/9a1f074b676e6cd0828811332e5781e8.avif?t=1770272806\" width=616 height=308 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103560/extras/c30d8b34d4b460a010b85fdbe9e3157b.avif?t=1770272806\" width=616 height=308 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103560/extras/e0a000488b4398aeac7c30d824093e01.avif?t=1770272806\" width=616 height=308 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103560/extras/077b42845e9c4f9bd3da194b73f0f845.avif?t=1770272806\" width=616 height=308 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103560/extras/36240a8409b40dd752d73880d9b3fabd.avif?t=1770272806\" width=616 height=308 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103560/extras/3b9942636296cf43e951fa1e6d7c9be6.avif?t=1770272806\" width=616 height=308 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>以及更多角色……</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103560/extras/eae9d66a77b8adf3e5e52781bf9b28d9.avif?t=1770272806\" width=616 height=308 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SideEye High</strong> 是为那些热爱经典冒险游戏、并准备好迎接更成熟体验的玩家打造的作品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
